Governors can pillage public resources with utter impunity but remain secure in their position. Yes, we have been dazed by the magic of muosho mmoja on Capitol Hill. The point here is that supporting the BBI offers corrupt officials complete immunity from persecution by the current administration. It was for this reason that Ngilu saw no fault in inciting the public against Kuria et al — for Kitui had become a slice of Kenya that she co-owned with the so-called Deep State.
Mr Musyoka is a former Vice-President and a man of distinguished career in politics and public service. He understands the importance of protocol in the functioning of the society.
Despite knowing that the Deputy President and the Principal Assistant to the President would attend the burial of Machakos Senator, Mutinda Kabaka, State House tasked Mr Musyoka with the responsibility of reading the President’s statement.
Public humiliation
This was yet another act of political foolery, which continues to dominate the post-handshake Kenya. Mr Musyoka is wrong in thinking the “system” could accept and embrace him if he contributes to the never-ending efforts to undermine the Office of the Deputy President and the public humiliation of the office holder. Rejecting this kind of madharau, mourners opted to walk out on the Kamba kingpin.



